<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Jan1932"><font color="red">28 January 1932</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I forgot to say Jolas is bringing out a <i>Transition</i> number which is to be an attack on Goethe (whose centenary it is) and a homage to me &hellip; I also bargained that he should print passages from the three recent attacks on me by Lennon, O.G. and &lsquo;One who knows him&rsquo;. </div>
